quran[14{c,v,t}:
109,1,Qul yaa-ai yuhal kaafiroon
109,2,Laa a'budu ma t'abudoon
109,3,Wa laa antum 'aabidoona maa a'bud
109,4,Wa laa ana 'abidum maa 'abattum
109,5,Wa laa antum 'aabidoona ma a'bud
109,6,Lakum deenukum wa liya deen
110,1,Iza jaa-a nas rullahi walfath
110,2,Wa ra-aitan naasa yadkhuloona fee deenil laahi afwajah
110,3,"Fa sab bih bihamdi rabbika was taghfir, innahu kaana tawwaaba"
111,1,Tab bat yadaa abee Lahabinw-wa tabb
111,2,Maa aghna 'anhu maaluhu wa ma kasab
111,3,Sa yas laa naran zaata lahab
111,4,Wam ra-atuh hamma latal-hatab
111,5,Fee jeediha hab lum mim-masad
